{"title":"争挖祖坟","authors":["池北偶　朱根华"],"dates":[{"year":2000,"month":2,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"争挖祖坟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱根华画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"匪徒盗墓猖狂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历代祖坟遭殃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你挖秦俑汉璧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他掘唐鼎宋缸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以往手工作业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今机械精良；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过去个人单干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在团伙登场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"偷窃大批古物，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走私变卖分赃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此风如不煞住，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遗产将被毁光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愧对列宗列祖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难求子孙原谅。（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}